{"type": "article", "id": 34008, "title": "Forever 21继续关店，以及，LV的World Tour系列包不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-02T02:23:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 3530, "name": "Forever 21"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 10699, "name": "L Brands"}, {"id": 18766, "name": "Snoop Dogg"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161102093910YVFEW4dAL7maIHpy.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/forever-21-to-shut-flagship-hong-kong-store-10694748/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Forever 21 将关闭香港旗舰店</b></a> | 据咨询机构 OC&amp;C Strategy 称，Forever 21 将关闭它在香港的旗舰店。这是继 Ralph Lauren 和 Coach 之后，又一个品牌在削减它在香港地区的门店数量。OC&amp;C Strategy 的合伙人 Jack Chuang 分析指出，高昂的店铺租金和不断衰退的大陆旅游消费，迫使这些品牌关闭了它们位于香港的店铺。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2016/11/01/l-brands-stock/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>维多利亚的秘密母公司股价大跌</b></a> |  L Brands 是“Victoria’s Secret”的母公司，受维密股价下跌 2% 的影响，L Brands 在昨日股价下跌了 7.88%。在今年全年，L Brands 的股价总共下跌了 25%。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/pandora-ramp-up-production-as-profits-see-40-growth-10695058/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>第三季度，Pandora 的营收大涨 18%</b></a> | 得益于在中国市场的良好表现，丹麦珠宝品牌 Pandora 在第三季度营收大涨了 18%，至 6.92 亿美元。利润上涨了 40%，至 2.11 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Nike 推出了“耐克”中文字样刺绣设计的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/nike-cortez-nai-ke\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike Classic Cortez Leather</a> 经典鞋款。其中，中文的“耐克”刺绣成为了亮点，这款鞋也是面向中国市场限定发售的，将于 11 月 9 日正式上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024610efiuRknAjmwSCZvT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024622lDQAq2TpJMiuyr4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703226\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024622pv8dCkbGDOJl7mBW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666129\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024622eKO4v5ZBLdH1DIMt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667082\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024628x5ORemwcLNofhB0p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">日本生活方式品牌 BEAMS 成立 40 周年所作的《Tokyo Culture Story》纸质版书刊正式推出，完整收录了 1976-2016 这四十年的东京时尚变迁。这本书目前已经在 <a href=\"http://www.beams.co.jp/item/tokyocultuart/music/30810037430\" rel=\"nofollow\">BEAMS 官网</a>上开售，售价为 1650 日元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024635doGaqAsbFShVcmv6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024644mN1cKUaM0ABTiQ8n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024650WriZ628pshdba09A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102024655awqRhKC064fdAN8L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>波士顿名店 Bodega 与 Vault by Vans 联手，带来了一款名为<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/bodega-x-vault-by-vans-sk8-hi-lx-instant-winner\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Instant Winner </a>的全新 Sk8-Hi LX 鞋款。这款鞋的鞋身使用了帆布、麂皮和皮革的拼接，后跟处的金色花朵刺绣成为点睛之笔，它将于 11 月 5 日在 Bodega 的线上店铺和门店正式发售，定价为 150 美元。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102094352LPRfJ3wMnamcCE0q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102094402t3CUx9YOHBJsNu8z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102094409pEvSMbcOmUzgqf40.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611020944091HVqUrzeCvAsJRhn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611020944095dBRZMwaQfDkgmlP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611020944177sMjrnScKzBCepWR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102094418JVY0mSC3oTfwlxaI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102094418Zpqg3BoTEf4SMDmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>LV 发布了值得玩味的 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/louis-vuitton-world-tour-collection/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">World Tour 最新系列</a>。这个系列以 LV 最经典的 Monogram 皮革包款为蓝本，汲取创意总监 Nicholas Ghesquiere 的旅行灵感，将酒店标签、汽车图章缝在 Monogram 图案上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100549ychfMjQNXK27Tz5i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100556lfIzPjXx6FDA17ZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100603KTmfq1tbeSly9B0L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100603wJPF6H4mR7picBjz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100603sNKEVDvWS0x9cMJH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100603GT8Zdy6HxJELqKlj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100603CNL78oWpBuMye3GP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100603xjts1R3wTfCNKYGM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100603XNriD7yLlnWpR8wY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100604e8DJLfNpRvzrcFZB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100604UZBakV3b6Xio90mc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/01/adidas-skateboarding-la-stories-collection-snoop-dogg-mark-gonzales/#slide-12\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 与 Snoop Dogg 及传奇滑手 Mark Gonzales 合作</a>，推出了新的联名系列 LA Stories。该系列包括限量款球鞋、连帽衫、长袖 shirt 等多款单品，在设计上颇有西部海岸的怀旧感。LA Stories 将于 12 月 5 日正式登陆 adidas 官方网站贩售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100613z3tUe52ArSIacMj6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100622DzefIdGsVQFXru7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110210062830g129qNZskKxMfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100637AEtxZ01ufzOpHno2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100637Nn6ujwkDqFrJt3pL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100644PKsz9l51cCeZXLJj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100653m2rjz0tdFBxZVDN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100653ZlBnP3NahEi9AOKm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161102100659jaHdmE05Xxngr3F6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}